%% Intended palette from STYLE-GUIDE.md: gate red, milestone green, feedback amber, process blue, artifact yellow, external gray.
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft
    Draft --> Submitted: ECR submitted
    Submitted --> UnderReview: Review started
    UnderReview --> Approved: Approved
    UnderReview --> Rejected: Rejected
    Rejected --> Draft: Rework
    Approved --> InImplementation: ECO released
    InImplementation --> Verified: FAI complete
    Verified --> Released: Effectivity issued
    Released --> [*]

    note right of Draft
        Initial authoring state
    end note

    note right of UnderReview
        Cross-functional assessment
    end note

    note right of Verified
        Quality evidence accepted
    end note
